    <h1>Explore Wikipedia Inside an Iframe</h1>
    <p>Below, you'll find a live view of Wikipedia embedded within an iframe. You can navigate and explore articles just as you would on the actual website.</p>

    <iframe src="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Main_Page" title="Wikipedia Main Page"></iframe>

    <p>Feel free to browse around! If you want the full experience, visit <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Main_Page" target="_blank">Wikipedia directly</a>.</p>

